# Walkthrough - Dashboard Sidebar & Navigation Enhancement

I have successfully implemented the dynamic sidebar system and updated the main navigation with product categories as requested. The application now features a consistent, premium dashboard experience for all user roles.

## Key Enhancements

### 1. Dynamic Dashboard Sidebar
A reusable [Sidebar.tsx](file:///d:/GroupProject/mallx-frontend/src/components/Sidebar.tsx) component has been created and integrated into all operational hubs. 

````carousel
![Desktop Sidebar View](file:///C:/Users/nk-noyon/.gemini/antigravity/brain/513cd81f-2436-4aed-9a46-9431b3c64bdc/admin_dashboard_check_1773744346467.png)
